      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="article-author pv-md col-sm-offset-3 col-sm-6">
                                    <a class="txt-dn txt-f1 txt-s3 txt-tu" href="/the-interpreter/contributors/articles/jack-sato">
                    Jack Sato
                </a>
                        </div>
